important;\">AND</span>&nbsp;user_guide_id&nbsp;=&nbsp;1;</div><div class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-30\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; background: rgb(53, 53, 53) !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">+---------------------+---------------------+---------------------+---------------+---------+------+</div><div class=\"crayon-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-31\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">|&nbsp;order_goods_id&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;sell_order_id&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;goods_id&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;user_guide_id&nbsp;|&nbsp;price&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;num&nbsp;&nbsp;|</div><div class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-32\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; background: rgb(53, 53, 53) !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">+---------------------+---------------------+---------------------+---------------+---------+------+</div><div class=\"crayon-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-33\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">|&nbsp;3792112143781859329&nbsp;|&nbsp;3792111966815784961&nbsp;|&nbsp;3792111950445416449&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1&nbsp;|&nbsp;3100.00&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2&nbsp;|</div><div class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-34\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; background: rgb(53, 53, 53) !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">|&nbsp;3792112160789762049&nbsp;|&nbsp;3792111966815784961&nbsp;|&nbsp;3792111951305248769&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1&nbsp;|&nbsp;5810.00&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1&nbsp;|</div><div class=\"crayon-line\" id=\"crayon-58bcd55c6f915094944361-35\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">+---------------------+---------------------+---------------------+---------------+---------+------+</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">从上面的试验我们可以看到原本在 &#39;分库分表(1)--基础表介绍&#39; 中的关联查询就能获得出订单的数据现在需要被拆为多个部分来查询(是不可避免的, 这样做也未必不是好事)。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">这里说一下我们为什么要使用ajax来获取并展现 &#39;订单商品&#39; 的数据：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">1、我们不知道 &#39;购买订单&#39; 的导购的分表是哪一个，因此我们需要便利查询出的每一条 &#39;购买订单&#39;，如果有10个订单就需要便利10次去获取对应导购是哪个分表。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">2、获得分表完之后还需要通过每个分表去关联 &#39;订单商品&#39; 获得商品信息。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">3、获得到以上信息或需要整合成一个列表返回给浏览器。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">通过上面一次性把说有数据返回给浏览器的方法，会影响到用户体验，让用户觉得很慢的感觉。并且需要写复杂的逻辑，难以维护。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-top: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">我们将查询时间放大，一个查是 1s 如果有10个订单 一次性完成就可能需要 11s 以上的时间才返回给浏览器。如果先将查询的订单返回给浏览器。看上去就只需要 1s就吧数据返回给浏览器了。</p><ul style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px 35px 0px 50px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 28.5px; list-style: square;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; marg