fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c25\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;OPP是指面向对象编程。主要是由1封装、2继承、3多态、4抽象四部分组成，它将数据及对数据的操作行为放在一起，作为一个相互依存、不可分割的整体——对象。使人们的编程与实际的世界更加接近，所有的对象被赋予属性和方法，结果编程就更加富有人性化。&nbsp;MVC是一种设计模式，也有人说是一种思想，我理解为PSR-4标准。由模型（model）视图（view）控制器（controller）完成的应用程序。由模型发出要实现的功能到控制器，控制器接受组织功能传递给视图。&nbsp;ThinkPHP&nbsp;3.2就是一个复杂的MVC框架加强版，对命名空间的支持以及有自动加载机制，并且有自己的助手函数，简单容易上手，但路由容易出错，控制器需要自己完善。&nbsp;ThinkPHP&nbsp;5.0和Laravel的非常像，比3.2增加了Composer支持。拥有更灵活的路由，更强大的查询语法，API开发友好。特别适合新手入门。</pre><p cid=\"c26\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c27\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">3、你怎么理解Run-time&nbsp;errors、Run-time&nbsp;warnings、Compile-time&nbsp;parse&nbsp;errors、Compile-time&nbsp;errors？（PHP内部错误机制）</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c28\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;Run-time&nbsp;errors:解释执行错误&nbsp;Run-time&nbsp;warnings:解释执行警告&nbsp;Compile-time&nbsp;parse&nbsp;errors:解析错误&nbsp;Compile-time&nbsp;errors:编译错误</pre><p cid=\"c29\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c30\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">4、请简单描述一个PHP文件缓存的实现机制（如Smarty的缓存机制原理）。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c31\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;将用户请求的内容存入一个静态文件中，当再次得到请求时直接从静态文件中输出，减少对数据库的访问；&nbsp;Smarty的缓存机制原理就是这样,开启Cache后，用户第一次请求，服务器响应，PHP文件经过编译后生成HTML静态页保存在相应目录中，有效期内，用户再次请求，直接从静态页输出。</pre><p cid=\"c32\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c33\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">5、请简述isset、is_null和empty三个函数的区别？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c34\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inheri