in-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;COOKIE：将会话信息的保存到浏览器端。&nbsp;&nbsp;SESSION：将会话信息保存到服务器端,安全性要高,负载均衡大时只用SESSION服务器压力大反应慢。&nbsp;SESSION的实现机制：PHP中首先开启SESSION_START--用户访问时检查是否有SESSIONID(有直接使用，没有就创建传到服务器，服务器会生成一个与之关联的SESSIONID返回给客户端)</pre><p cid=\"c65\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c66\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">10、有URL连接</span><span md-inline=\"url\" spellcheck=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><a href=\"http://www.itbeing.com/index.php?id=1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(65, 131, 196)\">http://www.itbeing.com/index.php?id=1</a></span><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">，请写一段代码提取该URL的域名信息（</span><span md-inline=\"url\" spellcheck=\"false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"><a href=\"http://www.itbeing.com\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(65, 131, 196)\">www.itbeing.com</a></span><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">）以及scheme协议（http）。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c67\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;$url&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;http://www.itbeing.com/index.php?id=1&#39;;&nbsp;$curl&nbsp;=&nbsp;parse_url($url);&nbsp;$str&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;host:&#39;.$curl[&#39;host&#39;];&nbsp;$str&nbsp;.=&nbsp;&#39;&#39;;&nbsp;$str&nbsp;.=&nbsp;&#39;scheme:&#39;.$curl[&#39;scheme&#39;];&nbsp;echo&nbsp;$str;</pre><p cid=\"c68\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c69\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">11、有如下代码，请从结果中选择正确的结果填入相应的位置。并且请简述Fatal&nbsp;error和Parse&nbsp;error两者的区别？（OOP和PHP内部机制）</span></span></p><p cid=\"c70\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c71\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">class&nbsp;Test{</span></span></p><p cid=\"c72\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c73\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"> public&nbsp;static&nbsp;function&nbsp;doTest(){</span></span></p><p cid=\"c74\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c75\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"> echo&nbsp;&quot;fortest\\n&quot;;</span></span></p><p cid=\"c76\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margi