nsolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;preg_match(&#39;/^[\\w\\-\\.]+@[\\w\\-]+(\\.\\w+)+$/&#39;,&nbsp;$email);</pre><p cid=\"c62\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c63\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">9、简单叙述一下COOKIE和SESSION的区别，以及SESSION的实现机制原理。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c64\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;COOKIE：将会话信息的保存到浏览器端。&nbsp;&nbsp;SESSION：将会话信息保存到服务器端,安全性要高,负载均衡大时只用SESSION服务器压力大反应慢。&nbsp;SESSION的实现机制：PHP中首先开启SESSION_START--用户访问时检查是否有SESSIONID(有直接使用，没有就创建传到服务器，服务器会生成一个与之关联的SESSIONID返回给客户端)</pre><p cid=\"c65\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c66\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"p