e\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">C.输出&nbsp;Parse&nbsp;error:&nbsp;syntax&nbsp;error,&nbsp;unexpected&nbsp;T_PAAMAYIM_NEKUDOTAYIM</span></span></p><p cid=\"c110\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c111\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">12、PHP中实现文件操作的几种方式？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c112\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;file()读取文件到数组&nbsp;file_get_contents()读取文件到字符串&nbsp;fopen()打开文件或者&nbsp;URL&nbsp;fwrite()写入文件&nbsp;fclose()关闭一个已打开的文件指针&nbsp;fgets()从文本指针中读取一行&nbsp;file_exists()检查文件或目录是否存在&nbsp;filesize()取得文件大小</pre><p cid=\"c113\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c114\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">13、请简要介绍一下你理解的AJAX原理？Ajax的优点缺点，简述缺点的相关解决方案，以及使用过的JavaScript&nbsp;Library（如Jquery）的相关特性。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c115\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">Ajax的工作原理相当于在用户和服务器之间加了—个中间层(AJAX引擎),使用户操作与服务器响应异步化。并不是所有的用户请求都提交给服务器,像—些数据验证和数据处理等都交给Ajax引擎自己来做,&nbsp;只有确定需要从服务器读取新数据时再由Ajax引擎代为向服务器提交请求。&nbsp;&nbsp;Ajax其核心有JavaScript、XMLHTTPRequest、DOM对象组成，通过XmlHttpRequest对象来向服务器发异步请求，从服务器获得数据，然后用JavaScript来操作DOM而更新页面。这其中最关键的一步就是从服务器获得请求数据。让我们来了解这几个对象。</pre><p cid=\"c116\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c117\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">14、JavaScript中如何将字符串转换成整数？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c118\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;parseInt();</pre><p cid=\"c119\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c120\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">15、简单叙述一下Mysql数据库中Varchar和Char数据类型的区别？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c121\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;varchar是可变长度，会根据字符串实际长度在有限指定范围内进行伸缩&nbsp;char是固定长度，你分配多大就占用多大&nbsp;在性能在char比varchar快，原因varchar可计算长度</pre><p cid=\"c122\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c123\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">16、简述MyISAM存储引擎和InnoDB存储引擎的主要区别？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c124\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;MyISAM不支持事务，也不支持外键；相反，InnoDB支持事务也支持外键；&nbsp;所以如果经常进行INSERTUPDATE操作时应该使用InnoDB。</pre><p cid=\"c125\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c126\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">17、请列出你使用过的Linux系统？以及常用的Linux编辑器？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c127\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;Ubuntu、macOS&nbsp;Sierra、centos&nbsp;图形系统：VS&nbsp;code、Sublime&nbsp;Text、Adobe&nbsp;Dreamweaver&nbsp;代码系统：vim、gedit</pre><p cid=\"c128\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c129\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">18、Linux下如何找出文件名为httpd.conf的文件路径？</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c130\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;which&nbsp;httpd.conf&nbsp;find&nbsp;/&nbsp;-name&nbsp;httpd.conf&nbsp;这个很耗资源、效率也低，是全盘遍列查找&n