cid=\"c170\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">某公司需要做一个内部管理系统，主要的功能有几个核心功能，员工数据管理、部门数据管理、任务数据管理、数据统计，详细功能需求如下：</span></span></p><p cid=\"c171\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c172\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">1）系统能够后台录入员工和部门数据</span></span></p><p cid=\"c173\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c174\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">2）系统能够后台录入任务数据</span></span></p><p cid=\"c175\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c176\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">3）系统能够后台将任务指定到员工</span></span></p><p cid=\"c177\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c178\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">4）系统能够统计员工所完成的任务数</span></span></p><p cid=\"c179\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c180\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">需要完成的任务：</span></span></p><p cid=\"c181\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c182\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">1）请跟进上述需求简单设计系统数据库表结构</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c183\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;CREATE&nbsp;TABLE&nbsp;user(id&nbsp;int&nbsp;null&nbsp;AUTO_INCREMENT&nbsp;PRIMARY&nbsp;KEY,name&nbsp;vachar(15)&nbsp;not&nbsp;null,id_part&nbsp;int)&nbsp;CREATE&nbsp;TABLE&nbsp;part(id&nbsp;int&nbsp;null&nbsp;AUTO_INCREMENT&nbsp;PRIMARY&nbsp;KEY,name&nbsp;vachar(30)&nbsp;not&nbsp;null)&nbsp;CREATE&nbsp;TABLE&nbsp;task(id&nbsp;int&nbsp;null&nbsp;AUTO_INCREMENT&nbsp;PRIMARY&nbsp;KEY,name&nbsp;vachar(50)&nbsp;not&nbsp;null,id_userint,state&nbsp;int,finish_time&nbsp;int)</pre><p cid=\"c184\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c185\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">2）请写一个sql语句查询员工A在某段时间内完成的任务数据记录。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c186\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;select&nbsp;*&nbsp;from&nbsp;task&nbsp;WHERE&nbsp;id_user&nbsp;=&nbsp;1&nbsp;and&nbsp;state&nbsp;=&nbsp;1</pre><p cid=\"c187\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0.8em;width: inherit;position: relative\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c188\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: block\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">3）请写一个SQL语句查询出某个部门内所有员工在某段时间内完成的任务数据记录。</span></span></p><pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block\" lang=\"\" cid=\"c189\" mdtype=\"fences\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;overflow: visible;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.9em;break-inside: avoid;background-image: inherit;background-position: inherit;background-size: inherit;background-repeat: inherit;background-attachment: inherit;background-origin: inherit;background-clip: inherit;border-radius: 3px;padding: 8px 1em 6px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-top: 15px;width: inherit;position: relative !important\">&nbsp;select&nbsp;*&nbsp;from&nbsp;auser&nbsp;WHERE&nbsp;auser.id_part&nbsp;=&nbsp;1&nbsp;and&nbsp;task.state&nbsp;=&nbsp;1</pre><p cid=\"c190\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-margin-before: 1rem;-webkit-margin-after: 1rem;margin-top